title: Compact Cord Protector & Cover for Floor by UT Wire
description:
UT Wire - Compact Cord Protector 

Wires across the floor of home, office or anywhere is more dangerous than you think, especially in high foot traffic areas. Cord protector is a great cable management solution to prevent unwanted accidents. UT Wire’s Compact Cord Protector is a single channel cord cover for floor to put those worries aside. Suitable for home and office when you need to run only one or two HDMI cables, telephone cords, or extension cord across the room or doorway. This soft rubber cable protector is very easy to cut and apply on the floor. Makes installation a breeze.  

"Simple Design, Big Solution"

For more information, please visit www.ut-wire.com/compact-cord-protector/
